intro:

[Pygments](https://pygments.org/) is a Python packages to syntax highlight
more than 300 programming languages and text formats. 

This PyGRAZ talk explains the basics of Pygments and then shows to to utilize
its API to quickly implement simple source code converters. It also
describes how to implements your own lexer.

